<BaseLayout title="About · spinup.fail">
  <div class="lang-en">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>If having good ideas was a superpower I'd be Batman. The ideas are wildly bad, but I execute them anyway. Mostly working on combat robots lately. Stay tuned for updates.</p>
    <p>This site has two sections:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Posts</strong>: directed write-ups about something I built or learned.</li>
      <li><strong>Updates</strong>: a running journal of project progress.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="lang-pt">
    <h1>Sobre</h1>
    <p>Se ter boas ideias fosse um superpoder eu seria o Batman. As ideias são absurdamente ruins, mas eu executo elas mesmo assim. Ultimamente trabalhando principalmente com robôs de combate. Fica de olho que vem mais.</p>
    <p>O site tem duas seções:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Posts</strong>: textos direcionados sobre algo que construí ou aprendi.</li>
      <li><strong>Updates</strong>: um diário de bordo do progresso dos projetos.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
